<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l18"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſchulde <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> Jr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> bürg ſeyt becʒalt <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> . des bıſher niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l19"><expan>beſcheh<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt Alſo manen wır eẅch <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> mıt dıſem brıef / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l20">noch <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> knecht mıt <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> pferd ſchıkt gen <expan>p<ex>er</ex>chnıg</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l21">in <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> windıſch hawſe . der da laıſte von pferden ʒu pferden vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l22">auch auſʒ der <expan>laıſtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> niht <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>ſchuldbr<ex>iefs</ex></expan> ſag bıs wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_177_r1l23">der <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſchulde becʒalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . Vnd getrawen <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> noch </ab>
